Republic Industries buys Anderson car dealership group . Republic Industries Inc said Tuesday it signed a definitive pact to buy the Anderson Dealership Group for about $ 40 million in Republic common stock . Republic said the acquisition gives the company a foothold in northern California . " Building from this base , Republic will add AutoNation USA used car megastores , and will fold in existing car rental operations , to create the foundation of a market cluster , " said Steven Berrard , president and co - chief executive . The Menlo Park , Calif . , Anderson dealership group includes Chevrolet , Honda , Isuzu , Lexus , Cadillac , and Oldsmobile dealerships . 
